# Post-Feature Refactor Trigger

After a major feature or multi-file change, run a short consistency pass before closing work.

## Trigger conditions

- multiple endpoints or data flows changed
- UI + API + DB touched in one feature
- large PR or broad refactor

## Required consistency checklist

- naming/style consistency with existing project patterns
- duplicate logic scan (extract or consolidate where reasonable)
- abstraction opportunities reviewed (avoid premature over-abstraction)
- dead code and stale files removed
- docs/styleguide references updated to match new behavior

## Communication requirement

- briefly report what was checked and what was changed
- if skipped for scope/time, state that explicitly and suggest a follow-up pass
